{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"API reference for "},{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" — the RevenueCat-backed "},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" conformer that the paywall plugin consumes."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","anchor":"Related-Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywallService"]},{"title":"Reference","anchor":"Reference","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/MockServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/UIComponentsReference"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" adapts "},{"code":"RevenueCat.Purchases","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to the "},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that "},{"code":"SwiduxPaywall.PaywallPlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" requires. It does one job: translate "},{"code":"CustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" into "},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (defined by "},{"code":"SwiduxPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") so the plugin can drive its state. Configuration of the RevenueCat SDK itself remains the caller’s responsibility."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For a step-by-step integration walkthrough, see "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". For the entitlement-mapping rules, see "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Library-target","type":"heading","text":"Library target","level":2},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Product: ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Import: ","type":"text"},{"code":"import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","type":"codeVoice"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"Package.swift","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":[".product(name: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\", package: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\"),"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Types","type":"heading","text":"Types","level":2},{"anchor":"docSwiduxRevenueCatPaywalldocumentationSwiduxRevenueCatPaywallRevenueCatPaywallService","type":"heading","text":"``doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywallService``","level":3},{"syntax":"swift","code":["public struct RevenueCatPaywallService: PaywallService {","    public init(","        entitlementID: String,","        permanentLicenseEntitlementID: String? = nil","    )","","    public func customerInfo() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot","    public func customerInfoStream() -> AsyncStream<EntitlementSnapshot>","    public func restorePurchases() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Value type. Holds two "},{"code":"String","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" identifiers and forwards every call to "},{"code":"Purchases.shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Safe to construct freely; cheap to pass into "},{"code":"PaywallPlugin","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Initializer","type":"heading","text":"Initializer","level":4},{"syntax":"swift","code":["public init(","    entitlementID: String,","    permanentLicenseEntitlementID: String? = nil",")"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"entitlementID","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — RevenueCat entitlement identifier that grants pro access. Surfaces as ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot.isPro","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when active.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — Optional secondary identifier for a lifetime \/ permanent entitlement. Surfaces as ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot.hasPermanentLicense","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when active. Pass ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if the app has no separate lifetime SKU.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywall\/configure(apiKey:appUserID:userDefaults:logLevel:entitlementVerification:purchasesAreCompletedBy:storeKitVersion:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" before constructing the service. The service does not configure RevenueCat itself, and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"type":"text","text":" traps if used unconfigured."}]}],"name":"Important","style":"important","type":"aside"},{"anchor":"customerInfo-async-throws-%3E-EntitlementSnapshot","type":"heading","text":"`customerInfo() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot`","level":4},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"One-shot fetch. Calls "},{"code":"Purchases.shared.customerInfo()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and maps the result."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Throws whatever the RevenueCat SDK throws ("},{"code":"ErrorCode.networkError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":".offlineConnectionError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", etc.). The plugin catches the error and dispatches "},{"code":".refreshFailed(message)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"customerInfoStream-%3E-AsyncStream%3CEntitlementSnapshot%3E","type":"heading","text":"`customerInfoStream() -> AsyncStream<EntitlementSnapshot>`","level":4},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Long-lived stream. Wraps "},{"code":"Purchases.shared.customerInfoStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and yields a new "},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for every change RevenueCat reports — purchase, refund, family-share update, sandbox renewal."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The stream finishes when the underlying RevenueCat stream finishes. The plugin’s "},{"code":".observeCustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" effect normally keeps it alive for the duration of the session; cancel by cancelling the consuming "},{"code":"Task","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", which terminates the stream and tears down the bridge."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"restorePurchases-async-throws-%3E-EntitlementSnapshot","type":"heading","text":"`restorePurchases() async throws -> EntitlementSnapshot`","level":4},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Calls "},{"code":"Purchases.shared.restorePurchases()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and maps the result. Throws whatever the SDK throws on error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The plugin’s "},{"code":".restorePurchases","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" action wraps this call and dispatches "},{"code":".customerInfoUpdated","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on success or "},{"code":".refreshFailed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Entitlement-mapping","type":"heading","text":"Entitlement mapping","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For every "},{"code":"CustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" the service receives:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isPro"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"entitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" active"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(next column)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"entitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" inactive or missing"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(next column)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID == nil"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"—"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" active"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"—"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"permanentLicenseEntitlementID"},{"type":"text","text":" inactive or missing"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"—"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"}]}]]]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Both flags are checked independently against the same "},{"code":"CustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". A user with both active subscription and lifetime entitlements gets both flags set. See "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for the reasoning behind the truth table."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Service Reference","role":"article"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/servicereference"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/RevenueCatPaywallService":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/revenuecatpaywallservice","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"RevenueCatPaywallService"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywallService","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" conformer backed by RevenueCat’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier",